				<img class="profile" src="${cPath }/assets/img/profile/defaultProfile.png" class="rounded-circle">
			</li>
			<li class="pl-4 bd-highlight" style="width: 80%">
				<a href="#" class="reply-writer">전수빈 </a>
				<span class="reply-date">작성 날짜 : 2021-12-24</span>
				<p>이 일감 나는 반댈일세!!</p>
				<details>
					<summary>답글 보기</summary>
					<ul class="pt-2 d-flex bd-highlight" data-repno="2">
						<li class="flex-shrink-1 bd-highlight align-items-center">
							<img class="profile" src="${cPath }/assets/img/profile/defaultProfile.png" class="rounded-circle">
						</li>
						<li class="pl-4 bd-highlight" style="width: 100%">
							<a href="#" class="reply-writer">전수빈 </a><span class="reply-date">작성 날짜 : 2021-12-24</span>
							<p>이 일감 나는 반댈일세!!</p>
						</li>
						<li class="bd-highlight" style="font-size: 20px;">
							<i class=" fas fa-ellipsis-v reply-menu" id="dropdownMenuButton" data-toggle="dropdown"></i>
							<div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
							    <a class="dropdown-item reply-update"><i class="fas fa-edit"></i>수정</a>
				   				<a class="dropdown-item reply-delete"><i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>삭제</a>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</details>
			</li>
			<li class="bd-highlight" style="font-size: 20px;">
				<i class=" fas fa-ellipsis-v reply-menu" id="dropdownMenuButton" data-toggle="dropdown"></i>
				<div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
					<a class="dropdown-item reply-create"><i class="fas fa-pen"></i>답글 작성</a>
				    <a class="dropdown-item reply-update"><i class="fas fa-edit"></i>수정</a>
				   	<a class="dropdown-item reply-delete"><i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>삭제</a>
				</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
</security:authorize>
